<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>CSS Box Model</title>
<style>
.box {
width: 300px;
content: "Sample Content";
padding: 20px; /* Padding */
border: 5px solid blue; /* Border */
margin: 30px; /* Margin */
background-color: #ecf0f1;
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}
h2 {
text-align: center;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>CSS Box Model Example</h2>
<div class="box">
This area represents the <strong>content</strong> of the box.
</div>

</body>
</html>
